-- U.K. Stocks Advance; InterContinental Hotels, ENRC Gain
-- B y   S r i n i v a s a n   S i v a b a l a n
-- 2012-08-07T07:41:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-07/u-k-stocks-advance-intercontinental-hotels-enrc-gain.html
U.K. stocks advanced for a third day,
led by a rally in shares of  InterContinental Hotels  Group Plc
and Eurasian Natural Resources Corp. Plc.  The volume of shares changing hands in companies listed on
the benchmark FTSE 100 Index surged to 77 percent above the
average in the past 30 days, data compiled by Bloomberg showed.  The FTSE 100 rose 0.3 percent to 5,826.11 at 8:39 a.m. in
London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
